Premier Giorgia Meloni chooses to congratulate his 'followers' > with a snapshot in which he sees it in the foreground. White shirt, smiled in front of the goal, the President of the Council - after the two American meetings with Donald Trump and J.D. Vance >- is sitting on a bench, behind it a floral composition.
"Good Easter to all of you. May it be a day of serenity, hope and happiness to share with the people you love. A sincere embrace, wherever you are," is Meloni's thought. >
