"The Easter Mass, a ray of sun, a smile thinking of my boys, the awareness of being lucky, the joy of knowing that there is a God who accompanies and protects us, the gratitude for your support and your affection. Good Holy Easter friends, hoping that in their egg everyone will find the serenity and fortune they want", writes on Instagram, commenting on a photo that portrays it, smiling, immediately after discarding a large chocolate egg.
